{"tid":2371806,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"文員涉831太子站管有彈弓及雷射筆被鄭念慈判囚1年 上訴被李運騰駁回","createTime":"2021-01-19T06:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T11:56:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e89cca98df6693fe7e6944b6995fbfb40638e5","tid":2371806,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13027&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrFyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=0d247467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13027</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第七庭<br />\n#李運騰法官 <br />\n#宣佈判決<br />\n#0831太子<br />\n<br />\n鍾(33) 🛑已服刑５個月<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器 <br />\n被控於2019年8月31日，於港鐵太子站內月台攜有攻擊性武器，即一個彈弓（即丫叉）、42粒螺絲帽，及一個能發出雷射光束的裝置。<br />\n<br />\n(2)無牌管有無線電通訊器材器具 <br />\n被控於同日同地無牌管有2套無線電收發器。<br />\n<br />\n背景： #鄭念慈裁判官 於2020年8月14日裁定２項控罪罪名成立，控罪(1)判處即時監禁12個月，控罪(2)罰款$5,000。 <br />\n<br />\n🛑法官駁回定罪及刑期上訴🛑<br />\n<br />\n🌟今天上訴人毋須出庭，判詞將上載到司法機構網站🌟<br />\n<br />\n判案書按此 (<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/ch/2020/HCMA000243_2020.docx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fch%2F2020%2FHCMA000243_2020.docx&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrFyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=b2a2d5c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/ch/2020/HCMA000243_2020.docx</a>)"},{"pid":"0333acdc51419be76aeb1f5ec23d069724c48233","tid":2371806,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"見到李運騰呢個閪名已經估到結果"},{"pid":"aae39ded61975846096389be319229f5f91651e1","tid":2371806,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k